{"tid":1795192,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊記］越南富國島五日四夜之旅","createTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T10:11:45.000Z","uid":171297,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3020aed214bce159865b712bdb9da21f33fda8","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"由於下個sem去東歐exchange<br />\n碌碌下機票見到vietjet air 香港飛富國島六百幾連稅<br />\n加上依家富國島短途停留免簽證<br />\n忍唔住要係走之前飛返轉東南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個trip因為16:55機去 11:55機返<br />\n基本上得三日full day 不過都好夠玩㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計曬機票住宿當地洗費港紙三千搞掂<br />\n喺窮遊好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BY3edBu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBY3edBu.jpg&h=f59a74ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xiUX29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xiUX29.jpg&h=a15200f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFHVHuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFHVHuQ.jpg&h=7b40e123&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5zUdBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5zUdBw.jpg&h=bffa5952&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0DBrWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0DBrWx.jpg&h=ab750642&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ONMn6WC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FONMn6WC.png&h=00c77234&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6GAoRop.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6GAoRop.png&h=414834c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHtNyBQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHtNyBQ.png&h=37336937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次打遊記 希望各位多多gchi同幫到有需要嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋記得不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f03a0d72429a5e8f773e1384c93dcd3a2c3e9b4","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"頭五張啲水印發生咩事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲唔好負皮我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053ad489dc69d2f2bc00ac3c4dab2a1fbc236fc6","tid":1795192,"uid":121544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f03a0d72429a5e8f773e1384c93dcd3a2c3e9b4","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"頭五張啲水印發生咩事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲唔好負皮我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:27:57.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚟緊依年都想去"},{"pid":"037a99b195d8575e123e534904c212e9d2811c5f","tid":1795192,"uid":312598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T19:24:09.000Z","msg":"富國島有咩野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665eb2dddc29212963a7b99aa50603bb2b2732e8","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T19:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚爛尾所以打定啲行程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">day1</span><br />\n機場&gt;resort<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">day2</span><br />\nSao Beach&gt;富國監獄&gt;過海纜車&gt;Night Market<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">day3</span><br />\n泥漿浴&gt;Starfish Beach<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;Aroma Massage <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">day4</span><br />\nVinpearl Land&gt;Rock Island Club&gt;Mango Bay On the Rock Restaurant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;轉第二間resort<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">day5</span><br />\nresort&gt;機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為富國島啲resort平靚正 所以頭三晚book咗間價位低啲嘅 最後一晚先book間villa with private pool諗住chill下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n敬請期待之後嘅遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3a145832f2e13d880516e3f3b8bc7f8e97ede6","tid":1795192,"uid":220719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T20:01:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"638e464bb2f4e4b267a27ede234de50342ace9d4","tid":1795192,"uid":264966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T22:57:17.000Z","msg":"路過，而家喺dusit&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n瞓醒食埋早餐就要返香港了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c902d0caa2a284542992935752d7c879cee032","tid":1795192,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"去越南有無叫雞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2045af8cc9fd39b0024830fd3997095281a0232a","tid":1795192,"uid":228440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"留名等睇食海鮮"},{"pid":"0e5e88c4c7869ed4f69bba45bfd09da4de61f93f","tid":1795192,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"果邊D靚酒店都幾平下<br />\n不過果邊D水都唔係幾清 又無咩玩 應該搞唔到好似布吉咁"},{"pid":"20f7526f93bd0726a8e654556ea07363b9eba852","tid":1795192,"uid":84848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"之前去開胡志明想去埋 <br />\n但唔記得自己張簽證唔出得境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced7605ac1d2f2217dcab699528eb0627a951db4","tid":1795192,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"留名 ，聽聞好伏"},{"pid":"8bf74ccaadf53099d6081084ef70fd4c0e4d8daa","tid":1795192,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"諗過去"},{"pid":"dcba045c63ba8dd200433852d8dfeab3000e39c3","tid":1795192,"uid":67279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"lm, 去過峴港覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"9285d910e936f9d76c4db1045d670c46b45a87dd","tid":1795192,"uid":264966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"準備上機，補充吓樓主冇去過嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有跟團出島，揀咗車+快艇團，<br />\n我去嗰日Mong 島啲唔清，能見度只有3-5米，游潛咗45min,有顏色嘅珊湖唔過10粒，唔多魚（游一分鐘可能見到4/5條，主要係細過手掌嘅魚仔）<br />\n跟住去May Rut島lunch, 一人一碟雞脾飯，加碟炸魚、炒通菜、灼魷魚十個人share食。島上啲狗勁有性格，只食海鮮，豪唯一嗰隻雞脾俾佢都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完飯後去埋Hon Thom島，呢個島啲reef靚小小，游咗一個鐘都見到十條八條大魚。不過呢水域係有人買起咗，放咗艘大船攪sea walking,我哋係&ldquo;唔小心&rdquo;游咗入去先睇到相對地靚小小嘅水（落水冇人帶，全程自己游，講定時間自己返上船）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國家公園&hellip;&hellip;大伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係條山路加啲高嘅樹，啲樹又冇乜特別，完全冇嘢睇，香港任何一個郊野公園都好行過佢同靚過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b17febc3512883d07ed51af94541b1c99788bfa","tid":1795192,"uid":264966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"上面係䌫車+快艇，唔知點解冇咗個&ldquo;纜&rdquo;字"},{"pid":"0378e7a7120e9d4b46c6375424a42b92dc2ea25e","tid":1795192,"uid":168020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f03a0d72429a5e8f773e1384c93dcd3a2c3e9b4","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T16:48:29.000Z","msg":"頭五張啲水印發生咩事...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲唔好負皮我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"唔知點解整水印會咁 好似po多過5張就會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db273550107970e10b459f5ba3e9bfb1d8623c3","tid":1795192,"uid":312205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"上兩個禮拜去過三日兩夜<br />\n幾啱hea嘅<br />\n啲酒店好l平<br />\n但佢啲發展只係啱啱起步<br />\n機場以南一片荒涼<br />\n直到嗰個纜車站先叫好少少<br />\n去到個島咩都冇<br />\n除咗落水hea真係冇野做<br />\n佢起緊個水上樂園預計21年搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個market 黎去都係幾款野食、餐廳<br />\n一式一樣<br />\n嗰陣去咁啱有國家隊比賽<br />\n成個島家家戶户係到播足球<br />\n成班人揸著電單車係條街開mic行黎行去<br />\n不過真係冇野玩<br />\n3日啱啱好<br />\n想落水加多日"},{"pid":"efa9f16abd70dac3c37877e8c7199ce838bb22e4","tid":1795192,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T18:34:35.000Z","msg":"好玩不？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d450e304792d8a230346f1110f3b5640f59004","tid":1795192,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f3194ead8c017b15c86eba1f8fabf1949496af","tid":1795192,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"咁快爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4269ec4d75c4d50764fad40228c33d0a9527ddcd","tid":1795192,"uid":48611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"已爛"},{"pid":"4232d91a51de65e339db4bada08222e009786a2f","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019就嚟完 希望大家出入平安 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始遊記之前長氣講多少少<br />\n由於VND面值好大 所以以下嘅貨幣冇特別提就係VND飛走三個零方便閱讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而當地因為啱啱開始發展其實都幾落後<br />\n主要交通工具喺的士同電單車<br />\n建議出發前download定Grab（=東南亞Uber）<br />\n最方便喺佢可以跟錶比現金 唔洗碌卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔用佢都可以睇下大概價錢<br />\n喺街邊截的士就唔洗被劏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且搭的士好平<br />\n我有兩日都喺叫resort幫手包咗兩日的士<br />\n一日$300港紙抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我食完個飯開始打day1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c96471b64cf3cd9ecb9c0c637dde55bd24077e","tid":1795192,"uid":171297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7c902d0caa2a284542992935752d7c879cee032","tid":1795192,"uid":149912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"去越南有無叫雞先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"叫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲好貴添<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c37cf41fb8873ee363d5be34bf7c70c38db534","tid":1795192,"uid":40985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"上星期去咗富國島 啲人幾純樸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗費又平"}]}